CHOLERA - UGANDA (05)
*********************
A ProMED-mail post
See Also
Cholera - Uganda 980110221717
Cholera - Uganda (02) 980205231117
Cholera - Uganda (03): correction 980207141542
Cholera - Uganda (04) 980407220736
Date: Tue, 28 Apr 1998 15:43:40 -0400
From: Dorothy Preslar <dpreslar@fas.org>
Source: Deutsche Presse-Agentur and local newspapers

The cholera epidemic that broke out earlier this year in villages near
Bundibugyo has claimed the lives of 20 persons within the past 3 days.
Bundibugyo is located in the mountains on Uganda's border with Democratic
Republic of Congo.
According to the Health Ministry, there have been about 500 deaths in this
epidemic.
